			Profile
			
			Prof.&nbsp;Zhi-ZhenHuangwasborninHangzhou,Zhejiang.HereceivedhisB.&nbsp;A.,&nbsp;M.&nbsp;S.and&nbsp;Ph.&nbsp;D.degreefromZhejiang&nbsp;University.He&nbsp;wasapostdoctoralfellow&nbsp;at&nbsp;theUniversity&nbsp;of&nbsp;Florida(1997-1999)and&nbsp;at&nbsp;theUniversityof&nbsp;Alabama(1999-2000).He&nbsp;was&nbsp;a&nbsp;professorat&nbsp;NanjingUniversityfrom2003to2010.Nowheisaprofessorand&nbsp;a&nbsp;doctoral&nbsp;instructorat&nbsp;ZhejiangUniversity.He&nbsp;has&nbsp;published&nbsp;over&nbsp;80&nbsp;papers,suchasinAngew.Chem.Int.Ed.,Chem.Commun.,Chem.Eur.J.,&nbsp;Org.Lett.and&nbsp;J.Org.Chem.He&nbsp;obtained&nbsp;aChineseYoung&nbsp;Chemist&nbsp;Award,aZhejiangYoung&nbsp;ScientistAward,etc.
			
				
